rows.label: qst700803_msg0001
rows.name:
Phew...
Finally! That should be the last of it...

rows.label: qst700803_msg0002
rows.name: Huh? Wh-who's there?!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0003
rows.name:
Heh heh heh...
Friends did well to sniff us out.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0004
rows.name:
Are you the ones who've been
littering the forest?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0005
rows.name:
That right! And may Ryuuryuu say, very
well done. It take person of many wiles
to disarm all traps of Four Muskerpon!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0006
rows.name:
But now we sorry to say that you
met your match. Ryuuryuu 1000%
certain that friends will fail!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0007
rows.name: Four Muskerpon? Never heard of you.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0008
rows.name:
Heh heh heh... Prick up ears and
listen well, friends. We only make
time for one extended introduction!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0009
rows.name: Ryuuryuu!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0010
rows.name: Kachakacha!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0011
rows.name: Yokuyoku!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0012
rows.name: Komemi!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0013
rows.name:
Though not of same blood,
we share same goal!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0014
rows.name:
We sink or we swim in same
boat, as one whole!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0015
rows.name:
We brothers in arms,
born under same star!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0016
rows.name:
To not hear of name is
thing quite bizarre!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0017
rows.name: Four Muskerpon!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0018
rows.name: Noponic Nine (Minus Five)!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0019
rows.name: Yokuyoku and Friends!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0020
rows.name: Meh! That right!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0021
rows.name: You're...all saying different things.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0022
rows.name:
Meh! We agreed yesterday would
go with Noponic Nine (Minus Five)!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0023
rows.name:
But it flow so badly! Cannot just tack
on "minus five" at end! What problem
with Four Muskerpon?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0024
rows.name:
Meh-meh-meh! Why so many dumb
names?! It clear "Yokuyoku and
Friends" is superior choice!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0025
rows.name:
Excuse me! Uh...whatever your name is.
Can we talk for a second?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0026
rows.name: Meh meh?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0027
rows.name:
Why exactly are you strewing litter
around everywhere?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0028
rows.name:
Because I think you should know that
a sweet old lady asked us to clean it up
for her so she could enjoy her walk.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0029
rows.name:
Could you please just stop this and go
somewhere else?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0030
rows.name: Meh? Granny Ofa is upset with us?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0031
rows.name: Granny...? You know her?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0032
rows.name: ...We sorry.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0033
rows.name: Will try to behave in future, meh...

rows.label: qst700803_msg0034
rows.name:
Oh...right. Well, I'm glad you
understand.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0035
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ]That was surprisingly easy...

rows.label: qst700803_msg0036
rows.name: ...As if!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0037
rows.name:
You thought we pack up and leave?
Think again!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0038
rows.name:
Muskerpon, to me! We retreat for
now, but we be back soon!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0039
rows.name: Big bro always know what to do!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0040
rows.name: Running away is also kind of victory!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0041
rows.name: Hey!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0042
rows.name: Those little nippers!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0043
rows.name: I think it's safe to let them go.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0044
rows.name: We've already singled them out.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0045
rows.name:
We need only identify them one by
one and this matter will be resolved.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0046
rows.name: Looks like they ran toward the capital.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0047
rows.name:
All right, then we'll ferret them out one
at a time, like Hugo said. We'd better
go and tell Ofa about all this!
